{"tid":543659,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)東方快車謀殺案 廣告牌殺人事件","createTime":"2018-01-28T17:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T20:14:43.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8cace3e082db8855eaf0187979a04c3314d9ae74","tid":543659,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=9YKHrMJwdctXi9TL31ylgDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=be70fa2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=9YKHrMJwdctXi9TL31ylgDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=284fb7b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bd/Murder_on_the_Orient_Express_teaser_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbd%2FMurder_on_the_Orient_Express_teaser_poster.jpg&h=5f68cb1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/49/Three_Billboards_Outside_Ebbing%2C_Missouri.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F49%2FThree_Billboards_Outside_Ebbing%252C_Missouri.png&h=0ad5970b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.比利時名偵探赫丘勒&middot;白羅打算暫時放下公事度假。他登上了由耶路撒冷開往伊斯坦堡的輪船，結識了家庭教師瑪莉&middot;德本海姆和阿布夫諾特醫生。到達伊斯坦堡，他碰到了現在當上知名的東方快車車長的故友柏克。然而，兩人重聚沒多久，一封從倫敦發來的電報召白羅到當地查案，於是伯克安排他坐上東方快車前往倫敦，展開為期三天的旅程。<br />\n第一天平安無事地度過了，但到了第二天晚上，惴惴不安的古董商山繆&middot;雷切特接近白羅，說他收到恐嚇信，邀請僱用白羅在行程期間保護他的人身安全。雷切特堅決地認為這封信出自之前向他買假油畫的客戶。白羅堅決地拒絕了， 向他表示自己是會對付惡人而不是保護他們的人。當晚，白羅正要睡覺，被雷切特房間的噪音吵醒，發現走廊上有一個穿著紅色和服的人影閃過，但是列車職員皮耶&middot;米切爾卻沒有發現。同時，一場雪崩把車頭撞至出軌，所有乘客被逼滯留在車上。白羅從床上摔下撞開房門，正好看見比尼亞米諾&middot;馬奎斯撿起由行李箱摔出來的一地照片<br />\n<br />\n2.海斯的女兒遭到姦殺，事發七個月後警方仍未找到兇手，於是在所居住密蘇里艾比鎮外三塊已荒廢看板上，買下一年的廣告將矛頭直指威洛比警長何以未將兇手繩之於法。然而，威洛比卻是頗受鎮民敬重的警長，並且已患末期癌症。他曾向海斯解釋因為DNA鑑證不合而無法捉拿疑兇<br />\n<br />\n1 25AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=9YKHrMJwdctXi9TL31ylgDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=5ba1b721\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=9YKHrMJwdctXi9TL31ylgDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=ed98cd9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbab28b07579e306413476b253b110ad45fff27","tid":543659,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0714f84f6e79dac9d45fd0176bf0ac52f3016222","tid":543659,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711e9d7007fe0ee8da5c2e77fa11c6ba6309